{"tid":273643,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"英國留學吹水區 6月號","createTime":"2017-06-06T17:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T10:30:58.000Z","uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fbc3852c849d4965e50b639199997204b9d425","tid":273643,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"簡介: <br />\n希望為各位喺英國留學嘅朋友開個位吹吓水、相認等等...同時希望提供少少英國留學嘅資訊。另外，仲有LIHKG 英國留學whatsapp group，有興趣請inbox<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Registration-for-lihkg-whatsapp-group-1667417386891749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRegistration-for-lihkg-whatsapp-group-1667417386891749&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=92563f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Registration-for-lihkg-whatsapp-group-1667417386891749</a><br />\n<br />\n資訊區: <br />\n俗稱[大台] UK Uni secret: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ukunisecrets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fukunisecrets&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4a71c703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ukunisecrets</a><br />\n<br />\n英國本土學生討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestudentroom.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestudentroom.co.uk&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=50dfdfac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestudentroom.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\n大學排名:<br />\nThe Complete University Guide <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4a1f2bd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thecompleteuniversityguide.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\nQS<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.topuniversities.com/qs-world-university-rankings\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.topuniversities.com%2Fqs-world-university-rankings&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=52c644ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.topuniversities.com/qs-world-university-rankings</a><br />\n<br />\n購物:<br />\n基乎所以生活所需二手用品都可以喺呢度搵到<br />\n租屋都得<br />\nGumtree:<br />\n<a href=\"http://guntree.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguntree.com&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c2140687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">guntree.com</a><br />\n<br />\n二手車 Autotrader:<br />\n<a href=\"http://autotrader.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fautotrader.co.uk&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d26699b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">autotrader.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\nHot uk deals: <br />\n<a href=\"http://hotukdeals.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotukdeals.com&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f00db8bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotukdeals.com</a><br />\n<br />\n租屋:<br />\nZoopla: <br />\n<a href=\"http://zoopla.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzoopla.co.uk&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d3d93b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">zoopla.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\nRightmove:<br />\n<a href=\"http://rightmove.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frightmove.co.uk&d=Ef8Irw5zTuLdDdePqpk34JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=20c7b247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">rightmove.co.uk</a><br />\n<br />\n問答區:<br />\n<br />\n住屋：<br />\n同人夾屋住 通常rent+bills喺咩range 入面？<br />\n個人意見-- rent 大約400至500 一個月(視乎地區、大細、幾多個人夾) ，bills 大約 50 一個月(都係視乎地區、你啲house mate) ，呢個數字只係約數，一切以閣下最後合約作準，本人不負任何法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n第一次去英國 有咩要注意？<br />\n第一次去英國帶少啲嘢去，啱啱好23kg就夠，基本上英國乜都有得賣。<br />\n<br />\nielts:<br />\n普通ielts定係UKVI ielts？<br />\n依家多數都需要UKVI，但詳細可以send個email俾uni問下。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n如有錯漏，請留言指正。會喺7月號post 改正，謝謝。"},{"pid":"9ec604e45660a4cc1a2f5bfa2bccb419ebd0e1da","